Related: therm

Heat is energy from the sun or fuel or decomposition.

Some sprays reflect solar energy to heat the atmosphere.

FVCool changes the PCI configuration data of a motherboard's chipset to allow Athlon/Duron CPUs to go into power-save mode, to reduce heat.

